{
  "texts": [
    "As we move, then, into the second quarter of the twenty-first century, we reject having to go about gaining a sense of belonging on our own terms.",
    "We instead urge institutional and shared responsibility for creating accessible spaces in which knowledge, experience and co-existence are given room to create and re-create evidence of belonging.",
